Flowmaster Part #817568 (American Thunder) 
Flowmaster Part #817633 (Outlaw)

Test Vehicle: 2015 Ram 1500 with a 5.7L engine.

Application:
Fits 2009 to 2016 Dodge/Ram 1500 trucks with a 5.7L V8 engine, fits 2 and 4 wheel drive models and all wheelbases.

Features:
These systems are designed to directly replace original mufflers using factory hangers and connections. With easy fit in mind, these units utilize mandrel bent tubing (where applicable) for maximum performance and include specially selected mufflers. Flowmaster American Thunder direct-fit mufflers deliver a moderate interior and exterior tone and are suited to the enthusiast who wants their performance to be heard without breaking the bank. Flowmaster Outlaw Series direct-fit mufflers are perfect for the person looking for a very deep and aggressive sound level outside and inside the vehicle. Like all Flowmaster systems, the benefits include improved throttle response, power and mileage. Designed for an easy fit, these systems include all necessary parts and hardware for easy installation.

Flowmaster Part #817725

Test Vehicle: 2015 Ford F-150 5.0L

Application:
2015-2016 Ford F-150 with 2.7L/3.5L EcoBoost, 3.5L TiVCT or 5.0L Engine, All Except Std Cab/Short Bed.

Features:
Flowmaster's American Thunder Cat-back exhaust system for the 2015-2016 Ford F150 is perfect for the person looking for an aggressive exterior sound level while maintaining a moderate interior sound with all of the performance benefits that you would expect from Flowmaster. This bolt on 409S stainless steel system for the 2.7L, 3.5L V6 and 5.0L V8 engines features 3.00" mandrel bent tubing that flows into a Super 40 muffler and then splits into dual 2.50" tailpipes. The system is finished off with dual 3.50" stainless steel tips that can exit out the rear or out the side. This system fits all cab and bed configurations except Standard Cab/Short Bed models. The exhaust system is manufactured in the USA and is covered by Flowmaster's Lifetime Limited Warranty. Designed for an easy fit, this system includes all necessary parts and hardware for installation.
